Atomsphere, a.k.a. atomchain is built without the mistakes of blockchain.

Blockchain is chaining of blocks, while Atomsphere is encapsulating of atoms.

Atomchain engineered and built on  the groundbreaking Atomchain Network (AtomNet), using the award-winning Atomchain Wallet (AtomWallet), executing on the novel Atomchain Virtual Machine (AtomVM), running on topnotch peer nodes (Atomic Nodes) based on the disruptive Atomchain Federated P2P Topology (AtomP2P) implementation...

Resilient to attacks, spoofs, malleability, flaws, malicious scripts, and errors.

Stable. Secure. Smart. Decentralized. Distinctive. Dogged.
